 begin="2:23.012" end="2:23.248">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请紧靠我身旁</span></p><p begin="2:24.583" end="2:29.060" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:24.583" end="2:24.934">Up</span> <span begin="2:24.934" end="2:25.292">in</span> <span begin="2:25.292" end="2:25.494">the</span> <span begin="2:25.494" end="2:26.604">clouds,</span> <span begin="2:26.604" end="2:26.893">I</span> <span begin="2:26.893" end="2:27.873">found</span> <span begin="2:27.873" end="2:28.118">my</span> <span begin="2:28.118" end="2:29.060">voice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在云端之上，我寻得自己的声音</span></p><p begin="2:29.702" end="2:34.180" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.702" end="2:30.032">Up</span> <span begin="2:30.032" end="2:30.336">past</span> <span begin="2:30.336" end="2:30.484">the</span> <span begin="2:30.484" end="2:31.612">shouts</span> <span begin="2:31.612" end="2:31.928">and</span> <span begin="2:31.928" end="2:33.267">broken</span> <span begin="2:33.267" end="2:34.180">noise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">冲破喧嚣与破碎的嘈杂</span></p><p begin="2:34.470" end="2:36.778" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:34.470" end="2:34.829">So</span> <span begin="2:34.829" end="2:35.132">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:35.132" end="2:35.486">let</span> <span begin="2:35.486" end="2:35.680">me</span> <span begin="2:35.680" end="2:36.778">fall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">别让我坠落</span></p><p begin="2:37.092" end="2:39.541" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:37.092" end="2:37.446">Where</span> <span begin="2:37.446" end="2:37.711">I</span> <span begin="2:37.711" end="2:38.083">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:38.083" end="2:39.541">belong</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">坠入不属于我的地方</span></p><p begin="2:39.983" end="2:44.788" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:39.983" end="2:40.241">I</span> <span begin="2:40.241" end="2:40.607">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:40.607" end="2:40.906">go</span> <span begin="2:40.906" end="2:41.830">back</span> <span begin="2:41.830" end="2:42.218">and</span> <span begin="2:42.218" end="2:43.120">lose</span> <span begin="2:43.120" end="2:43.548">it</span> <span begin="2:43.548" end="2:44.788">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我无法重回过往失去一切</span></p></div></body></tt>